TITLE: Episode 17 - Dirty Maharrey
DESCRIPTION: Welcome to our first MLGA Chat without Ryan Burgett. We have Mike Maharrey of the Tenth Amendment Center fame. We had a great conversation with Mike about the constitution, violence, Christianity, and it is well worth the listen.
